;; Pinned small universe — ~300 liquid US equities spanning 11 GICS sectors.
;;
;; Curated on 2026-04-17 for step 1 of the backtest scale-optimization plan
;; (PR #396). See dev/scripts/pick_small_universe/README.md for the selection
;; contract; see dev/plans/backtest-scale-optimization-2026-04-17.md §Step 1
;; for the why.
;;
;; This file is hand-curated in its initial cut because the selection script
;; requires data/inventory.sexp, which isn't present in the CI environment
;; where this commit was authored. The script in
;; trading/backtest/scenarios/pick_small_universe/ is the reproducible path
;; and should be used for subsequent refreshes once data is accessible.
;;
;; Selection criteria (matched by the hand curation):
;;   * 11 GICS sectors, >=20 symbols each where possible
;;   * S&P 500 constituents with known 2018-2023 price history
;;   * Known historical Weinstein cases (NVDA, MSFT, META, TSLA, etc.)
;;
;; Composition (as of 2026-04-17):
;;   Communication Services:    20
;;   Consumer Discretionary:    28
;;   Consumer Staples:          24
